2c:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Kommunal xizmatlar kalkulyatori O'zbekistondagi barcha asosiy kommunikatsiyalar uchun oylik to'lovlarning to'liq qiymatini hisoblaydi: elektr energiya, tabiiy gaz, sovuq va issiq suv, oqava suv (kanalizatsiya), chiqindilarni chiqarish va domofon. Barcha tariflar 2025–2026-yilning amaldagi stavkalari bo'yicha hisoblanadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda o'rtacha oylik kommunal to'lovlar (2025–2026): Toshkentda 2 xonali kvartira — 400 000-800 000 so'm (yoz) va 600 000-1 200 000 so'm (qish); 3 xonali kvartira — 500 000-1 000 000 so'm (yoz) va 800 000-1 500 000 so'm (qish); gaz isitishli xususiy uy — 300 000-600 000 so'm (yoz) va 1 500 000-3 000 000 so'm (qish)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Oddiy kvartira uchun kommunal to'lovlar tarkibi: elektr energiya — 30-40%, gaz — 20-40% (mavsumga qarab), suv — 15-25%, chiqindi chiqarish — 5-10%, domofon/xizmat — 5%."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":